 "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/1/c/1cad1bd2-7c56-4ce0-99a6-b2a49c1288dd.jpg?1782682506", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/msc/191/arcane-signet?utm_source=api", "local": "img/arcane/0bc7f093-bef0-4f1a-852c-4b75ebf54838.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Cinderheart Giant", "set": "KHM", "html": "What fire giants lack in <mark>arcane</mark> prowess, they make up for with reckless, explosive rage.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/e/4/e4802e6c-6921-4dac-bf44-7e09d6942b71.jpg?1782705474"}, {"card": "Prodigal Pyromancer", "set": "TSR", "html": "&quot;Learn to burn!&quot;\n—Institute of <mark>Arcane</mark> Studies motto", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/f/cf16600a-c2a5-49e4-89e2-260cfaf58b52.jpg?1782741822"}, {"card": "Seat of the Synod", "set": "EOC", "html": "Lumengrid, site of the Knowledge Pool, source of vedalken <mark>arcana</mark>.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/7/57a194b3-2899-4dee-977a-c77df0b94dfe.jpg?1782685596"}, {"card": "Dark Ritual", "set": "MSC", "html": "&quot;Behold! The most <mark>arcane</mark> powers of the multiverse are mere tools in service of Doom&#x27;s ambition.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/1/11e12a84-e7be-4afc-a230-c2e644743fa8.jpg?1782681991"}, {"card": "Spellgorger Weird", "set": "CLU", "html": "Freed from their respective labs, the two weirds formed a partnership, feeding on the <mark>arcane</mark> energies of war.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/b/9ba52955-2ab9-48a4-bb12-6127bdef1909.jpg?1782693505"}, {"card": "Scroll Thief", "set": "DDT", "html": "Kapsho merfolk have infiltrated fortresses as remote as the desert citadel in Sunari in their relentless quest for <mark>arcane</mark> knowledge.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/7/a7caae7e-9b88-4428-b9e3-86cb8c84bd65.jpg?1782748504"}, {"card": "Jodah, Archmage Eternal", "set": "2X2", "html": "&quot;Chronicles across the ages describe Jodah. They likely refer not to one mage, but to a family or an <mark>arcane</mark> title.&quot;\n—Arkol, Argivian scholar", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/3/73c18cb4-96b1-4af2-912e-974e22877ede.jpg?1782737813"}, {"card": "Vodalian Mage", "set": "FEM", "html": "&quot;Vodalian Mages are remarkable. Their merchants bring them <mark>arcane</mark> lore and devices from across the seas.&quot;\n—Lydia Wynforth, Mayor of Trokair", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/1/c107e82b-134a-4f2b-98c2-6537fae6a50d.jpg?1782722023"}, {"card": "Uncovered Clues", "set": "DGM", "html": "The Implicit Maze winds through Ravnica, connecting <mark>arcane</mark> landmarks of all ten guilds.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/d/9dd24556-994f-4480-835e-11d4443f0700.jpg?1782714024"}, {"card": "Fathom Fleet Firebrand", "set": "XLN", "html": "As she charges into battle, her <mark>arcane</mark> tattoos stir and crawl like fiery serpents.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/2/52280963-ba5b-4735-b5cb-67866f8624c9.jpg?1782710409"}, {"card": "Aether Flash", "set": "7ED", "html": "As the foul beast appeared, <mark>arcane</mark> lightning crackled around it.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/8/780f9197-e910-4c7a-bb4b-2c4a94903c39.jpg?1782719703"}, {"card": "Omnispell Adept", "set": "GRN", "html": "She memorized every <mark>arcane</mark> text in the Ismeri Library by the time she was sixteen. Now she quizzes sphinxes in her spare time.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/e/1/e17664df-e8ba-464d-b338-3e671d2d7f0e.jpg?1782709151"}, {"card": "Crystal Ball", "set": "C18", "html": "It glints with <mark>arcane</mark> truths to those who know how to glimpse them.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/d/3/d344d88f-a63b-4593-990f-af6346cad91a.jpg?1782709266"}, {"card": "Lozhan, Dragons' Legacy", "set": "CLB", "html": "She channels myth and memory into waves of deadly <mark>arcane</mark> force.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/e/fe604232-19da-4331-a6f2-ddb004f1dd90.jpg?1782701175"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Sideswipe", "set": "CHK", "html": "You may change any targets of target <mark>Arcane</mark> spell."}, {"card": "Kami of the Painted Road", "set": "CHK", "html": "Whenever you cast a Spirit or <mark>Arcane</mark> spell, this creature gains protection from the color of your choice until end of turn."}, {"card": "Evermind", "set": "SOK", "html": "(Nonexistent mana costs can&#x27;t be paid.)\nDraw a card.\nSplice onto <mark>Arcane</mark> {1}{U} (As you cast an <mark>Arcane</mark> spell, you may reveal this card from your hand and pay its splice cost. If you do, add this card&#x27;s effects to that spell.)"}, {"card": "Soul of Magma", "set": "CHK", "html": "Whenever you cast a Spirit or <mark>Arcane</mark> spell, this creature deals 1 damage to target creature."}, {"card": "Elder Pine of Jukai", "set": "SOK", "html": "Whenever you cast a Spirit or <mark>Arcane</mark> spell, reveal the top three cards of your library. Put all land cards revealed this way into your hand and the rest on the bottom of your library in any order."}, {"card": "Skyfire Kirin", "set": "SOK", "html": "Flying\nWhenever you cast a Spirit or <mark>Arcane</mark> spell, you may gain control of target creature with that spell&#x27;s mana value until end of turn."}, {"card": "Prosper, Tome-Bound", "set": "AFC", "html": "Deathtouch\nMystic <mark>Arcanum</mark> — At the beginning of your end step, exile the top card of your library. Until the end of your next turn, you may play that card.\nPact Boon — Whenever you play a card from exile, create a Treasure token."}, {"card": "Faithful Squire // Kaiso, Memory of Loyalty", "set": "BOK", "html": "Whenever you cast a Spirit or <mark>Arcane</mark> spell, you may put a ki counter on this creature."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/b/6bd611b7-7bd3-4a76-bd69-34a7235965ae.jpg?1782718182", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/6/b/6bd611b7-7bd3-4a76-bd69-34a7235965ae.jpg?1782718182", "card": "Sideswipe"}}